column17:
Product Description

Step in vogue with this charming clutch wallet. This TLB piece looks like a chic little bag on one side and a Wall Street goddess on the other. The versatility of it comes from its uniquely designed front that has nouveau contrast coloured 'Fruit Loop' detailed stitching and a charming flap. Available in colours that are as contrasting as your personality and with thoughtfully laid out spaces for all your weekday and weekend essentials. Large enough to grab and go and compact enough to bundle into your handbag.
